snippet.title: [ SOLARIS X SOLAR INCEPTION ] malice ... - solar inception
snippet.description:
playing solaris while listening to the song "malice ..." off of the full-length, "resurrection," from my solo project, solar inception. 

solaris is available for download as a pay-what-you-want game, for windows PCs with Mac and Linux ports on the horizon. please consider donating.
http://a6productions.itch.io/solaris
buy the game for $15 or more to be able to download "WITHIN SOLARIS," a 12-track compilation album including an exclusive single made using the sounds from solaris.

solar inception - resurrection:
http://solarinception.bandcamp.com/album/resurrection

http://twitter.com/TRONMAXIMUM
